Interface NEATEvolutionStrategy<D,T>

Type Parameters:

All Superinterfaces:
EvolutionObject, EvolutionStrategy<D,T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractNEATEvolutionStrategy, NEATEvolutionStrategyImpl
public interface NEATEvolutionStrategy<D,T>
extends EvolutionStrategy<D,T>

The NEATEvolutionStrategy interface extends the EvolutionStrategy interface, and represents the main EvolutionObject for the NEAT algorithm.
